songs.lyrics:

Hey, hey, hey[x4]
Shoulder to lean on
Hey, hey, hey
(You gotta have the strength)

My heart don’t wanna see the sun rise
Don’t know why
I’ll be filled with fear
He done got me up
songs.title: Ball of Clay
